comment_data.body:
Thanks for the report @parasthekoder.  We just released a new version of the Flutter Plugin (27.0) that may address this issue.   At the same time, make sure you're on the latest flutter (`flutter upgrade` from the command line, or Tools > Flutter from the IDE).  Let us know if the issue persists after upgrades.

Cheers!
